Template: SkyPanel/install_type
Type: select
Choices: panel, node
Description: Is this installation a full panel or only a node?
  Select `panel` if you would like to have the full experience.
  Select `node` if you are deploying this only as a node.

Template: SkyPanel/create_user
Type: boolean
Description: Do you wish to create a new admin user?

Template: SkyPanel/email
Type: string
Description: Email to assign to new user

Template: SkyPanel/username
Type: string
Description: Username to assign to new user

Template: SkyPanel/password
Type: password
Description: Password to assign to new user

Template: SkyPanel/password_confirm
Type: password
Description: Confirm password

Template: SkyPanel/password_mismatch
Type: note
